    <string name="register_privacy_notice">By creating an account you accept our <![CDATA[<u><font color="#006A67">Privacy Policy</font></u>]]></string>
    <string name="onboarding_privacy_notice">By continuing you accept our <![CDATA[<u><font color="#006A67">Privacy Policy</font></u>]]></string>
    <string name="privacy_policy_content"><![CDATA[
**PRIVACY NOTICE — TouristNotify (LUPITA)**

Controller: José Ibarra / TouristNotify
Contact: joseinnit04@outlook.com

**Data we collect**
• Email address and password (authentication)
• Nickname / display name (personalization)
• Profile photo (optional)
• Precise location (geofencing and map)
• Check-in history (visited places with date/time)
• Favorites and saved routes
• Reviews and ratings
• Prompts sent to the AI service (Google Gemini) to generate routes

**Who we share your data with**
• Google Firebase (Auth, Firestore, Storage, Analytics, Crashlytics)
• Google Maps Platform
• Google Gemini AI (only the text of the route generation prompt)
• OpenWeatherMap (only geographic coordinates of Álamos, Sonora)

**Your rights (GDPR Art. 15-21 / LFPDPPP Art. 22-27)**
You have the right to: Access, rectify, erase, port, and object to the processing of your data.
Exercise your rights from Menu → My Profile (edit, export data, delete account).

**International transfers**
Data is processed on Google LLC servers (USA) under EU Standard Contractual Clauses.

**Retention**
Data is kept while your account is active. When you delete your account, all your data is removed from our systems within 30 days.

**Changes to this policy**
We will notify you of significant changes through an in-app notice.

NOTE: This is a provisional notice. The final legal text is pending review by legal counsel.
